'''A_RailWait'''

(no parameters)

Does nothing. The full sourcecode for this codepointer is merely a comment:
 DEFINE_ACTION_FUNCTION(AActor, A_RailWait)
 {
    // Okay, this was stupid. Just use a NULL function instead of this.
